  (str content) (str `2
LIST OF AMENDING ACTS
1. The Andhra Pradesh Reorganisation (Amendment) Act, 2014 ( 19 of 201 4 ).
2. The Andhra Pradesh Reorganisation (Amendment) Act, 2015 ( 12 of 201 5 ).
3. The Andhra Pradesh Reorganisation (Amendment) Act, 20 26 (7 of 20 26).
_______
LIST OF ABBREVIATIONS USED
Cl., cls...... for Clause, clause s.
Ins......,, Inserted.
Notifn......,, Notification.
S., ss......,, Section, section s.
Sch......,, Schedule.
Subs......,, Substituted.
w.e.f......,, with effect from.`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str sourcePage) (int 2)
obj_root_law_sections_3:
